All Classes

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CollectionActivity
    The CollectionActivity class displays the user's current QR code collection and rank.
    CollectionTest
    The CollectionTest class contains unit tests for the CollectionActivity.
    CommentActivity
    This activity displays the comments associated with a particular QR code.
    CommentTest
    The CommentTest class is used to test the comment functionality of the application
    DBUpdate
    The DBUpdate class is responsible for updating the scores of users in the Firestore database.
    ExampleInstrumentedTest
    Instrumented test, which will execute on an Android device.
    ExampleUnitTest
    Example local unit test, which will execute on the development machine (host).
    FriendPageActivity
    The FriendPageActivity class represents the activity for displaying the user page of a friend.
    MainActivity
    This class defines all the controller on the main page.
    MainActivityTest
    Test class for MainActivity.
    MapsActivity
    This class is used to display a map and add markers to it.
    modelCode
    This class represents the data of a QR code, including the score, latitude, longitude, hash code, and photo.
    modelLocation
    This class is used to store the location of the QR code along with the QR code itself.
    modelMessage
    Represents a message object with a sending date, a receiving date, a sender, a receiver, and a unique ID.
    modelRank
    Represents a rank object that contains a list of users sorted by their rank.
    modelUser
    The modelUser class is used to store the user's information including their ID, name, contact information, total score, and the list of codes that they have scanned.
    MyProfileTest
    This class represents a unit test for the CatchTheCode app.
    QRcode
    represent the QR code and corresponding information
    QRCodeActivity
    The QRCodeActivity class displays the details of a specific QR code, including its name, image, comments, and the users who have scanned it.
    QRCodeActivityTest
    This class is used to test the functionality of QRCodeActivity.
    QRInfo
    This class represents the QR code information.
    ScanFailMsg
    This class represents the Scan Fail Message that is displayed after a failed QR code scan.
    ScannedBarcodeActivity
    represent a qr code scanner that can automatically scan the qr code
    scanTest
    This class contains the test cases for scanning QR codes functionality in the app.
    ScoreBoardActivity
    Represents a scoreboard activity and its functionalities
    ScoreBoardTest
    Test class for the ScoreBoardActivity.
    SearchActivity
    The SearchActivity class extends AppCompatActivity and overrides onCreate to create the activity and set the content view to the searching_page layout.
    SearchFriendsActivity
    This class runs the search friends list page.
    SearchGeoActivity
    This class runs the search geolocation list page.
    SearchTest
    The SearchTest class contains test cases for testing search functionality.
    SplashActivity
    The SplashActivity class is responsible for showing a splash screen for 3 seconds before We DID NOT implement this due to technical difficulties.
    UserActivity
    This class represents the user activity and corresponding activities.
